Senior Legal Counsel, ECM team of Global Bank - 5 years+
Location:  Singapore
An experienced equity capital markets lawyer is required to support the deal team within this leading international bank. You will be required to run ECM transactions and provide day-to-day advice for the ECM team as well. Ideally you will have 5 or more years of ECM experience gained from a top firm or in-house with another bank/FI. A good understanding of ECM financial products is required.
Please contact Julia Lee at JLegal in Singapore on +65 6818 9701 or submit your resume to julia@jlegal.com quoting Ref no: JLL – IS 1370
